        -command "from maya import cmds\n\ndigit = 2\n\nfor joint in cmds.ls(type=\"joint\"):\n    x = round(cmds.getAttr(f\"{joint}.tx\"), digit)\n    y = round(cmds.getAttr(f\"{joint}.ty\"), digit)\n    z = round(cmds.getAttr(f\"{joint}.tz\"), digit)\n    \n    cmds.setAttr(f\"{joint}.translate\", x,y,z)\n" 
